  <description>Stems 0.5–1.5(–2) dm. Basal leaves: petiole 0.5–2.5(–3.5) cm; blade oblanceolate to obovate in outline, 0.3–1.5(–2) cm × 2–4(–7) mm, margins usually lyrate-pinnatifid, rarely dentate or entire; lateral lobes obtuse. Cauline leaves 0–4; blade linear to oblong. Fruiting pedicels 3–7 mm. Flowers zygomorphic; sepals 0.5–0.8(–1) × 0.4–0.6(–0.8) mm; petals oblong to obovate, abaxial pair 1.5–2.5 × 0.6–1 mm, adaxial pair 0.5–1 × 0.3–0.4 mm; stamens 6, tetradynamous; filaments 0.8–1 mm, (basal appendage white, ca. 1/2 its length); anthers 0.1–0.2 mm. Fruits 3–4.5 × 3–4.5 mm; style ca. 0.1 mm. Seeds 1–1.2 × 0.9–1 mm. 2n = 36.</description>
